 />\n<br />\n黨鐵咁都仲有AA? 危害乘客安全喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"133fbe747a1995121794ef5457a367d2cd78ffc8","tid":1559648,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZd64DE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZd64DE.jpg&h=33235d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tFcr4DF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtFcr4DF.jpg&h=4f032819&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43b88313c216985147beda2755f99af655bc1b31","tid":1559648,"uid":8873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:04:29.000Z","msg":"前線保護自己，美國消滅共產黨需時10年要你哋長期助攻<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1555452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1555452</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"83e2834d9e93a693cb2f109ab41c5d9beddc97fc","tid":1559648,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:06:15.000Z","msg":"港鐵呢d仆街直接a啦"},{"pid":"08e236ea94058009f2179d9034595b9f1ca24308","tid":1559648,"uid":111998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:12:21.000Z","msg":"嗱, 關政府事<br />\n唔好入示威數"},{"pid":"5111b8f10ee638892be31f2badfcf8727454ba21","tid":1559648,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T02:24:51.000Z","msg":"共產黨維穩鐵路有限公司"}]}